{"tid":2188841,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"新西蘭男子死於武漢肺炎　5月底以來首宗死亡病例","createTime":"2020-09-04T13:09:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-04T13:14:57.000Z","uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"8c40a1739fe1dd9447ddfa627ce3be38474af0b0","tid":2188841,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T13:09:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1547923-20200904.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1547923-20200904.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=HMiOmB7b1AqxO%2BCwCPl1cVLn0p5rLcPQxw7X33U7JQw%3D&h=2d2bbb17\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1547923-20200904.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=cef97f43\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1547923-20200904.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n新西蘭一名年約50歲男子，死於武漢肺炎，是當地最年輕的死亡病例，亦是自5月28日以來，首宗死亡個案。<br />\n<br />\n死者是奧克蘭超過150名患者中的其中一名，去世前在深切治療部留醫。<br />\n<br />\n衛生官員說知道民眾感到憂慮，但他必須指出，可能有更多國民，死於武漢肺炎。<br />\n<br />\n總理阿德恩說，在奧克蘭地區實施的「半封鎖措施」，有效期延長兩星期。"},{"pid":"75181608a979ea71af7318fadaf2344370129ad9","tid":2188841,"uid":8014,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T13:13:04.000Z","msg":"問刁仔索償<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b93bb3b84dd07c46d4a00fc8096dee448ad44a7","tid":2188841,"uid":143474,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T13:14:57.000Z","msg":"紐西蘭之前先100 日無本地感染都可以再爆一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}